  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Gladio Mori is a physics-driven fighting game that redefines the gladiator arena. Whether playing solo or challenging others in multiplayer battles, you’ll wield razor-sharp weapons and unleash unique moves in brutal, tactical combat. Every decision, swing, and step matters as you carve your path to victory.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2689120/extras/867483f80b4fcb1c6b5d8faa34dc98f5.poster.avif?t=1772541464\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2689120/extras/867483f80b4fcb1c6b5d8faa34dc98f5.webm?t=1772541464\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Multiplayer</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Take on opponents in intense online battles with up to 4 players or enjoy the action locally with split-screen gameplay. Prove your skill and adaptability in every fight as you rise to claim victory in the arena.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2689120/extras/9c260f04c2f46bb2239e5fd40c1e1091.webp?t=1772541464\" width=616 height=49 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Organ-Based Damage System</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Forget health bars—combat in Gladio Mori is as brutal as it is precise. Damage to muscles, arteries, and vitals directly impacts your ability to fight:</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Injured Muscles</strong> weaken your strikes.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Severed Arteries</strong> cause you to bleed out.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Pierced Vitals</strong> mean instant death.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Precision and strategy are your greatest weapons.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2689120/extras/b5e97daf375354b98fc10d9e52d8826e.poster.avif?t=1772541464\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2689120/extras/b5e97daf375354b98fc10d9e52d8826e.webm?t=1772541464\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Authentic Weapons and Armor</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >No magical gear here—just realistic weapons and armor that behave as they should. Plate armor blocks strikes, but exposes weak points. Find openings in your opponent’s defenses or risk being outmatched.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2689120/extras/54085257f4078740f36eef3d59799664.poster.avif?t=1772541464\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2689120/extras/54085257f4078740f36eef3d59799664.webm?t=1772541464\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>In-Game Move Editor</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Unleash your creativity with a fully customizable move editor. Control your character’s physical body to craft unique animations:</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Design efficient and devastating attacks.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Recreate iconic moves from your favorite films or games.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Experiment with wild, unpredictable maneuvers—it's up to you.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2689120/extras/e759da8944b2aad7c466a41c3bf69108.poster.avif?t=1772541464\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2689120/extras/e759da8944b2aad7c466a41c3bf69108.webm?t=1772541464\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Community-Created Moves</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Not an animator? No problem. Explore movesets shared by other players or mix and match individual moves to create a style that’s entirely yours. The community fuels the creativity in Gladio Mori.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2689120/extras/fc62e9e8efbf261ca7eec65da9e0eef5.poster.avif?t=1772541464\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2689120/extras/fc62e9e8efbf261ca7eec65da9e0eef5.webm?t=1772541464\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Enter the Arena</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Every battle in Gladio Mori is a test of strategy, skill, and ingenuity. Forge your fighting style, exploit weaknesses, and prove your worth in the ultimate arena.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The gladiator's path awaits—are you ready?</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Gladio Mori is a physics-driven fighting game that redefines the gladiator arena. Whether playing solo or challenging others in multiplayer battles, you’ll wield razor-sharp weapons and unleash unique moves in brutal, tactical combat. Every decision, swing, and step matters as you carve your path to victory.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2689120/extras/867483f80b4fcb1c6b5d8faa34dc98f5.poster.avif?t=1772541464\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2689120/extras/867483f80b4fcb1c6b5d8faa34dc98f5.webm?t=1772541464\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Multiplayer</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Take on opponents in intense online battles with up to 4 players or enjoy the action locally with split-screen gameplay. Prove your skill and adaptability in every fight as you rise to claim victory in the arena.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2689120/extras/9c260f04c2f46bb2239e5fd40c1e1091.webp?t=1772541464\" width=616 height=49 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Organ-Based Damage System</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Forget health bars—combat in Gladio Mori is as brutal as it is precise. Damage to muscles, arteries, and vitals directly impacts your ability to fight:</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Injured Muscles</strong> weaken your strikes.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Severed Arteries</strong> cause you to bleed out.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\